articles.description: Chris Clemons knocked down five 3-pointers and scored 25 points as Campbell took over sole possession of third place in the Big South Conference by cruising past Longwood, 88-54 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Campbell alone in 3rd in Big South, beats Longwood 88-54

articles.description: Donta Hall leads the Crimson Tide with 17 points and 11 rebounds while Collin Sexton adds 16 points in a 28-point rout of the No. 15 Volunteers.
articles.headline: Alabama crushes No. 15 Tennessee

images.caption: Donta Hall leads the Crimson Tide with 17 points and 11 rebounds while Collin Sexton adds 16 points in a 28-point rout of the No. 15 Volunteers.
images.name: Alabama crushes No. 15 Tennessee

articles.description: Desmond Ringer had 17 points and seven rebounds, Ross Cummings added 16 points with four 3-pointers and Mercer beat Chattanooga 84-75 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Mercer tops Chattanooga 84-75

articles.description: Jaren Lewis had 20 points and 17 rebounds on Saturday and Abilene Christian led by double digits for most of the second half in an 80-69 win over Incarnate Word.
articles.headline: Lewis leads Abilene Christian over Incarnate Word 80-69

articles.description: Jordon Varnado scored 23 points with 13 rebounds and Troy defeated Little Rock 82-64 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Varnado leads Troy with double-double in 82-64 win

articles.description: Johnathan Stove had a career-best 28 points and Bryce Washington added 18 with 13 rebounds as Louisiana recovered from its only Sun Belt Conference loss by getting past Georgia Southern 102-91 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Louisiana recovers from only league loss, beats Ga. Southern

videos.description: Garrison Brooks steals an inbound pass allowing Sterling Manley to bank in the shot for North Carolina.
videos.headline: UNC turns steal into Manley bucket

videos.description: North Carolina uses some nice passing to setup a one-handed jam for Cameron Johnson.
videos.headline: Good ball movement leads to Johnson dunk

videos.description: Pittsburgh's offensive rebound leads to Marcus Carr draining a shot from way downtown as the shot clock expires.
videos.headline: Carr hits deep-3 pointer to beat shot clock

videos.description: Luke Maye's great feed allows Christian Johnson to score on the fast break plus a foul for North Carolina.
videos.headline: Maye nice transition pass leads to Johnson and-1 layup

videos.description: Joel Berry II misses a 3-pointer but Garrison Brooks grabs the rebound to score plus a foul for North Carolina,
videos.headline: Brooks scores and-1 after getting offensive board

videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson hammers down a big dunk with one hand off a missed shot.
videos.headline: Pinson rattles the rim with putback dunk

videos.description: Theo Pinson throws a perfect pass down court to Kenny Williams who scores on the fast break for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Pinson's great outlet pass leads to Williams' lay-in
